gobblin.data.management.retention.version.finder

Class DateTimeDatasetVersionFinder

  • java.lang.Object
    • gobblin.data.management.retention.version.finder.DatasetVersionFinder<TimestampedDatasetVersion>
      • gobblin.data.management.retention.version.finder.DateTimeDatasetVersionFinder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    VersionFinder<TimestampedDatasetVersion>

    public class DateTimeDatasetVersionFinder
extends DatasetVersionFinder<TimestampedDatasetVersion>
    DatasetVersionFinder for datasets based on path timestamps. Uses a datetime pattern to find dataset versions from the dataset path and parse the DateTime representing the version.
